WEBVTT

00:01.412 --> 00:02.832
<i>Einstein may be the brightest mind</i>

00:02.833 --> 00:03.932
I have yet taught.

00:03.933 --> 00:04.990
PERNET: <i>He's a menace!</i>

00:04.991 --> 00:06.158
(yelling)

00:06.159 --> 00:07.206
You are skipping classes

00:07.207 --> 00:08.908
<i>and challenging your instructors.</i>

00:08.909 --> 00:10.543
What I want to know, sir, is why?

00:10.544 --> 00:12.478
My name is Professor Philipp Lenard.

00:12.479 --> 00:14.382
- Herr Professor.
- Mileva Maric.

00:14.383 --> 00:16.617
<i>One doesn't lose track of
the sole woman in the room.</i>

00:16.618 --> 00:18.653
MILOS: <i>She's up all night,
filling her brain with things</i>

00:18.654 --> 00:20.054
<i>I can't begin to understand.</i>

00:20.055 --> 00:22.223
Then how do you know
she understands them?

00:22.224 --> 00:24.099
EINSTEIN: <i>I'm head over heels in love</i>

00:24.100 --> 00:25.767
<i>with your mind. Be my partner.</i>

00:25.768 --> 00:27.270
<i>In life, in love,</i>

00:27.271 --> 00:29.471
<i>in endless scientific pursuit.</i>

00:29.472 --> 00:31.574
PAULINE: <i>How is Marie?
Everyone is quite excited.</i>

00:31.575 --> 00:33.476
<i>- About what?
- The courtship, of course...</i>

00:33.477 --> 00:35.577
- <i>the potential of it!
- I'm going to be a professor.</i>

00:35.578 --> 00:37.585
I will think for thinking's sake.

00:37.586 --> 00:38.653
That is the most indulgent thing

00:38.654 --> 00:40.522
- I've ever heard.
- Oh, don't leave

00:40.523 --> 00:41.424
like this, Albert.

00:41.425 --> 00:43.292
Liar! How could you be

00:43.293 --> 00:45.677
so careless with my heart?!

00:45.678 --> 00:47.044
Physics should be an adventure.

00:47.045 --> 00:48.178
Herr Einstein, enough!

00:48.179 --> 00:49.347
<i>Fail him if you must.</i>

00:49.348 --> 00:51.082
<i>I am no longer concerned for his future.</i>

00:51.083 --> 00:52.916
- Miza!
- Hello, Papa.

00:52.917 --> 00:55.621
<i>I am so sorry, Papa. I failed you.</i>

